stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PROVISIONING_PENDING: employee-created received
    PROVISIONING_PENDING --> INVITED: Firebase identity provisioned and employee active
    PROVISIONING_PENDING --> DISABLED: employee inactive
    INVITED --> ACTIVE: invitation accepted or Firebase password setup completed
    ACTIVE --> LOCKED: lockout threshold reached
    ACTIVE --> DISABLED: employee disabled
    ACTIVE --> ARCHIVED: employee archived
    INVITED --> DISABLED: employee disabled
    INVITED --> ARCHIVED: employee archived
    LOCKED --> ACTIVE: admin unlock
    LOCKED --> DISABLED: employee disabled
    LOCKED --> ARCHIVED: employee archived
    DISABLED --> INVITED: employee reactivated; assumed new invitation
    ARCHIVED --> INVITED: employee reactivated; assumed new invitation
    ARCHIVED --> [*]: retention/deletion policy outside authentication scope
